	<tr><td background="/lotr/gfx/mom/whi_07.gif"></td>
		<td bgcolor="#FFFFFF" background="/lotr/gfx/mom/whi_08.gif"><font class="bfont"><table width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="4" cellspacing="0"><tr><td colspan="2"><font class="h1font">Constantly Threatening: TTT Block 6th Place</font></td></tr><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Rating</Font></TD><TD><table width='93' border='0' cellspacing='0' cellpadding='0'><tr><td background='/lotr/gfx/5star.gif'><img src='/lotr/gfx/trans.gif' width='1' height='25'></td></tr></table><font size=1>(4.63)</font> | <A HREF="/lotr/decks/decks.php?reviews=29852&PHPSESSID=...328fedb22570524062aeb1303">Read Reviews</A></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Author</font></TD><TD><font class="bfont"> <A HREF="http://www.decktech.net/lotr/main/mpage.php?member=8874">Adam "ramolnar" Molnar</A></FONT> <font class="afont"> <a href='http://www.decktech.net/lotr/main/mpage.php?member=8874&sub=1'> (Subscribe to this member)</a></font></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Description</Font></TD><TD> </TD></TR><TR><TD COLSPAN="2" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="bfont"> The deck I used to finish 6th in Towers Block at the World Championships.  It&#39;s Ents, Hobbits, and full site stacking Dunland. 
</FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Submitted</Font></TD><TD><font class="bfont"> July 30, 2003</FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Cards</Font></TD><TD> </TD></TR><TR><TD COLSPAN="2" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="bfont"> Frodo, Tired Traveller <br />
<a href="javascript:card_browser(182)">The One Ring, The Ruling Ring</a> <br />
 <br />
Merry, Learned Guide <br />
Pippin, Woolly Footed Hobbit <br />
Quickbeam <br />
 <br />
Plains of Rohan <br />
Rohirrim Village <br />
Golden Hall <br />
White Mountains <br />
Deeping Wall <br />
Hornburg Hall <br />
Cavern Entrance <br />
Ring of Isengard <br />
Palantir Chamber <br />
 <br />
3 Sam, Samwise the Brave <br />
2 <a href="javascript:card_browser(180)">Hobbit Sword</a> <br />
4 Severed His Bonds <br />
4 Swiftly and Softly <br />
2 Knocked on the Head <br />
3 Gandalf Greyhame <br />
2 Mithrandir Mithrandir <br />
3 Lindenroot <br />
2 Ent Horde <br />
2 Ent Avenger <br />
1 Skinbark <br />
3 Crack into Rubble <br />
 <br />
4 Hides <br />
3 War Club <br />
2 Burn Every Village <br />
1 Dark Fury <br />
2 Saurman Rabble Rouser <br />
1 Constantly Threatening <br />
1 Wild Man Raid <br />
2 Over the Isen <br />
2 Hillman Horde <br />
3 Wulf <br />
4 Hillman Tribe <br />
